I probably wouldn't have stayed at someplace so upscale had I not lucked out with a great rate on Expedia ($112), but I was thrilled that I was able to because the location can't be beat.	Not enough drawer space would be my only complaint and the bathroom was a bit small for the King Premium room.	As I mentioned we had wanted a bit of luxury to recover from our jetlag and the VP fitted this excellently.	We were a little leery about what we would end up with based on the price but we couldn't have been happier with our stay and recognize now what a great deal it was.